            "content": "<h2>How To Choose The Right Combination Of Ring Shape And Cut </h2><p>Choosing the right diamond is all about the right harmony of the shape and the cut you choose. Having said that, it is also important to consider the lifestyle you have. We have curated a simplified table for you that eas_based on your style. </p>",
